## Required Database Tables (PostgreSQL Schema)

To maintain standard snake_case naming in PostgreSQL and camelCase in TypeScript, we'll use Prisma's `@map` and `@@map` attributes.

### 1. `users` Table
- `id`: `String` (UUID, primary key)
- `name`: `String`
- `email`: `String` (unique index)
- `password`: `String` (hashed)
- `role`: `Enum` (`admin`, `manager`, `rep`)
- `isActive`: `Boolean` (default: true)
- `avatar`: `String` (optional initial string like 'SC')
- `createdAt`: `DateTime` (default: now)
- `updatedAt`: `DateTime` (updated on modification)

### 2. `contacts` Table
- `id`: `String` (UUID, primary key)
- `firstName`: `String`
- `lastName`: `String`
- `email`: `String`
- `phone`: `String` (optional)
- `company`: `String` (optional)
- `jobTitle`: `String` (optional)
- `status`: `Enum/String` (`active`, `inactive`, `blocked`, default: `active`)
- `source`: `Enum/String` (`website`, `referral`, `cold_outreach`, `event`, `partner`, `other`, default: `other`)
- `tags`: `String[]` (native PG text array)
- `notes`: `String` (optional text)
- `assignedToId`: `String` (optional, foreign key to `users`)
- `createdById`: `String` (foreign key to `users`)
- `createdAt`: `DateTime` (default: now)
- `updatedAt`: `DateTime` (updated on modification)

### 3. `deals` Table
- `id`: `String` (UUID, primary key)
- `title`: `String`
- `contactId`: `String` (optional, foreign key to `contacts`, cascades on delete or set null)
- `company`: `String` (optional)
- `value`: `Float`
- `stage`: `Enum/String` (`new`, `contacted`, `demo_scheduled`, `proposal_sent`, `negotiation`, `closed_won`, `closed_lost`)
- `priority`: `Enum/String` (`low`, `medium`, `high`, default: `medium`)
- `expectedCloseDate`: `DateTime` (optional)
- `closeReason`: `Enum/String` (`won`, `lost`, `no_decision`, `cancelled`, or empty)
- `closedAt`: `DateTime` (optional)
- `assignedToId`: `String` (optional, foreign key to `users`)
- `createdById`: `String` (foreign key to `users`)
- `notes`: `String` (optional text)
- `createdAt`: `DateTime` (default: now)
- `updatedAt`: `DateTime` (updated on modification)

### 4. `activities` Table
- `id`: `String` (UUID, primary key)
- `type`: `Enum/String` (`call`, `email`, `meeting`, `note`, `task`)
- `subject`: `String`
- `description`: `String` (optional text)
- `contactId`: `String` (optional, foreign key to `contacts`)
- `dealId`: `String` (optional, foreign key to `deals`)
- `assignedToId`: `String` (optional, foreign key to `users`)
- `dueDate`: `DateTime` (optional)
- `completed`: `Boolean` (default: false)
- `completedAt`: `DateTime` (optional)
- `createdById`: `String` (foreign key to `users`)
- `createdAt`: `DateTime` (default: now)

