## API Endpoints

All APIs (except public login/register) will require a `Bearer <token>` in the `Authorization` header.

### 1. Authentication (`/api/auth`)
- `POST /api/auth/register` - Create a new user (admin/manager/rep).
- `POST /api/auth/login` - Verify password and return User details + JWT access token.
- `GET /api/auth/me` - Return the current user payload decoded from JWT.

### 2. Contacts (`/api/contacts`)
- `GET /api/contacts` - List contacts with filter queries (`q`, `status`, `source`).
- `GET /api/contacts/:id` - Get detail of a contact, including linked deals count and activities count.
- `POST /api/contacts` - Create new contact (requires validation).
- `PUT /api/contacts/:id` - Update contact fields.
- `DELETE /api/contacts/:id` - Delete contact.
- `POST /api/contacts/bulk` - Perform bulk action: `{"action": "assign" | "tag" | "delete", "ids": string[], "data": any}`.

### 3. Deals (`/api/deals`)
- `GET /api/deals` - Retrieve all deals (optionally filtered by stage).
- `GET /api/deals/:id` - Retrieve a single deal.
- `POST /api/deals` - Create a deal.
- `PUT /api/deals/:id` - Update deal parameters.
- `PUT /api/deals/:id/stage` - Update a deal's stage (Kanban drop/update).
- `DELETE /api/deals/:id` - Delete deal.

### 4. Activities (`/api/activities`)
- `GET /api/activities` - Get activities, optionally filtered by `contactId`, `dealId`, or type.
- `POST /api/activities` - Create activity.
- `PUT /api/activities/:id` - Update activity parameters.
- `PUT /api/activities/:id/complete` - Toggle completion status.
- `DELETE /api/activities/:id` - Delete activity.

### 5. Dashboard (`/api/dashboard`)
- `GET /api/dashboard/metrics` - Aggregated stats for the dashboard tiles (Totals, Conversion, Close counts) and stage value distributions.

